# 4. HONEY in 東京

Member of ASRUN: Thank you all for coming to see us today!
Member of ASRUN: ASRUN's Tour of Japan: “HONEY” in Tokyo is just getting started!
Haruka: Some of you out there may be going through some sad or tough times and have a lot on your minds right now...
Haruka: But we want you to forget about all of that today! Let's make the most of our time together!
Minori: ...!
Minori: (I... I knew it... Haruka really is the best...!)
Haruka: So, here we go!
Chihiro: Oh, it's this song... The one from your DVD...
Minori: We practiced it a lot together!
Minori: Haruka just gave me some words of encouragement, so it's time for me to do the same for her!
Minori: Hey! Hey!
Member of ASRUN: Hm...? I can't hear you! Is that all you got?!
Haruka: You guys can do better than that, right?!
Minori: Yes we can, Haruka!!
Minori: Hey!! Hey!!
Haruka: Nice! That's what I like to hear!
Haruka: Now, it's time for us to respond!
Haruka: ♪————!!!
Minori: (Whoa...)
Minori: (It's like our cheering and Haruka's singing are coming together as one song.)
Minori: (Practicing this at home was fun, but this is something else...)
Minori: (Plus...)
Haruka: Everyone! Can you hear me?! Let's keep having more fun together!
Minori: (Haruka really is incredible. I can't take my eyes off her. She's sparkling even more compared to when I see her on TV...)
Minori: (All that doubt I felt just a second ago... It's all gone!)
Haruka: ♪————!
Minori: (The way she smiles and sings... It fills me with so much joy and energy.)
Minori: I wanna keep singing with her...
Minori: (I'm gonna do everything I can to make her singing, dancing and overall performance even more exciting... And then...)
Minori: (I'm gonna show her how I feel... I'm gonna show just how much I admire her!)
Minori: Haruka...
Minori: You're the best!!!
Member of ASRUN: Thanks for keeping up with us until now!
Haruka: Unfortunately, our next song is going to be our last one for today...
Minori: What?! The last one...?!
Chihiro: Time really flew by...
Haruka: As sad as it is to say goodbye to one another, we promise to cap off this amazing day with an unforgettable performance! Are you all ready?!
Minori: I'm ready, Haruka! I promise to cheer my lungs out!
Haruka: Alright, here comes the song you've all been waiting for...!
Minori: *Gasp* Does that mean...?
Chihiro: Their new song...?!
Haruka: “Maidenly Honey Mustard”!
Minori: Whoa...! All the glow sticks just turned orange...!
Minori: But this is their first time performing this song... How did they all know what to do...? Also...
ASRUN Fans: Noooo!! ASRUN, I'm not ready to go home yet!!
ASRUN Fans: I'll keep rooting for you!! I promise to go to your shows in Fukuoka and Sendai!!
Haruka: Thank you all for your kind thoughts! Let's make this song a moment to remember!
Minori: (This song... It's like everyone's a part of it... Not just Haruka and the others. The entire audience as well...)
Chihiro: I underestimated you, Minori...
Minori: What?
Chihiro: Before, I honestly didn't fully comprehend what you liking idols and being a fan of a specific one meant...
Chihiro: I sort of brushed off what you've been saying until now. But after seeing them for myself...
Chihiro: I understand why you love ASRUN and Haruka Kiritani so much... Because... Because...
Chihiro: They're so cool!
Minori: Chi...
Haruka: Come on, everyone! Louder!
Chihiro: Hey! Hey!
Minori: Oh...
Minori: (Even though she said she felt really embarrassed when we were practicing at my house...)
Member of ASRUN: Is that all you got?! I know you can do better than that!
Member of ASRUN: How are you guys doing?! Tell us! Show us how you really feel!
Minori: How we really feel...?
ASRUN Fans: This is awesome!!
ASRUN Fans: I'll follow you wherever! I'm your fan forever!!
Haruka: Thank you...
Haruka: We heard you loud and clear!
Minori: Oh...
Minori: They heard us...
Minori: (Oh, is that it...?)
Minori: (Now I see... This place, this atmosphere... It was all designed to bring us and the idols together.)
Minori: (The way we cheered for ASRUN, and the way they responded to us...)
Haruka: Some of you out there may be going through some sad or tough times and have a lot on your minds right now...
Haruka: But we want you to forget about all of that today! Let's make the most of our time together!
Minori: (It's like everyone here is becoming one... And they're making it all happen.)
Minori: They understand my worries and concerns, and are cheering me on to keep going.
Minori: I feel this bond forming between us... It feels like they're rooting for me.
Minori: That's why we're all this excited...
Minori: (And standing at the center of all that...)
Minori: (The heart of this venue and atmosphere is...)
Haruka: ♪————!
Minori: (She's all sweaty after doing so many laps around the stage... But she's still sparkling...)
Minori: (She keeps smiling while responding to our calls, while singing and dancing with everything she has.)
Minori: (The way she smiles and sings... It fills me with so much joy and energy.)
Chihiro: They're so cool!
Minori: ...
Minori: I... I had no idea...
Minori: This is what it means to be a real idol.
Minori: It was ASRUN's agency too, so I was really hoping that I'd get in. I even made sure to write, “I want to become a super idol who's an amazing singer and dancer, like Haruka!”
Minori: And I already figured out how to do the dance for this song! I think I can do it on demand now.
Minori: Does this mean I have real talent...? Do I have what it takes to become an idol?
Minori: I'm nothing like them...
Minori: Just because I learned to dance a little, that doesn't mean I'm ready to become an idol.
Haruka: ♪————!
Minori: Copying them is one thing, but this is completely different...
Minori: I've decided that I'm gonna become an idol just like Haruka, so I need to be more optimistic!
Minori: It just isn't that easy, huh...?
Minori: It's not impossible...
Minori: Right now, there's probably no way that I can become an amazing idol like Haruka...
Haruka: ♪————!
Minori: But I want to be up there... I want to stand on that stage.
Minori: Haruka encouraged me, so I wanna find a way to do that for someone else.
Minori: I want to, but...
Minori: Huh? Wh-What was that...?
Chihiro: Minori, wake up!
Chihiro: It's Haruka! She's coming towards us on a little trolley!
Minori: What...?
Minori: W-Wait... Haruka's so close...
Minori: ...!
Minori: (Is she looking at me...?)
Minori: (Her beautiful eyes... They're seeing me...?)
Haruka: Are you having fun?
Minori: Huh...?
Haruka: Let's make the best of our time together and make this a moment to remember.
Haruka: So... Just clear your mind.
Haruka: And let's sing together!
Minori: Oh...
ASRUN Fans: *Scream* Haruka!!!
ASRUN Fans: We love you!!
Chihiro: Th-That was so awesome...! She was right there...
Minori: T-Together...
Chihiro: Minori...?
Haruka: Let's sing!
Minori: Yeah...
Minori: (I wanna sing with her... While standing next to her...)
Minori: (I wanna sing and spread hope to lots and lots of people...!)
Minori: Just wait, Haruka!! I'll be up there with you soon...!!
Minori: One day! I promise...!!
Haruka: Thanks, everyone!
